<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to VirdisPay</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .features {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .feature-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .feature-icon {
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
        }
        .step {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .kyc-status {
            background: #fff3cd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üåø VirdisPay</div>
            <div class="subtitle">Professional Crypto Payments for High-Risk Industries</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Welcome to VirdisPay, {{firstName}}!
            </div>

            <p>Thank you for joining VirdisPay, the leading crypto payment processor designed for high-risk industries. Your business <strong>{{businessName}}</strong> is now ready to accept secure, compliant cryptocurrency payments.</p>

            <div class="features">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #333;">What you get with VirdisPay:</h3>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <span class="feature-icon">‚ö°</span>
                    <span><strong>99.98% Gas Savings</strong> with Smart Payment Routing</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <span class="feature-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</span>
                    <span><strong>Built-in Compliance</strong> for high-risk industry regulations</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <span class="feature-icon">üîí</span>
                    <span><strong>Non-Custodial Security</strong> - you keep your private keys</span>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <span class="feature-icon">üåø</span>
                    <span><strong>High-Risk Friendly</strong> - no banking restrictions</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            {{#if kycStatus}}
            <div class="kyc-status">
                <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #856404;">üìã Next Step: Complete KYC Verification</h4>
                <p>To start processing payments, you'll need to complete our KYC (Know Your Customer) verification process. This ensures compliance with industry regulations and protects your business.</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1976d2;">Your Next Steps:</h3>
                {{#each nextSteps}}
                <div class="step">{{this}}</div>
                {{/each}}
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button">Access Your Dashboard</a>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Need Help?</strong> Our support team is here to help you succeed. Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a> or visit our help center.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>VirdisPay</strong> - Professional Crypto Payments for High-Risk Industries</p>
            <p>¬© {{currentYear}} VirdisPay. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="{{siteUrl}}/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> | 
                <a href="{{siteUrl}}/terms-of-service">Terms of Service</a> | 
                <a href="{{siteUrl}}/compliance">Compliance</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>



